{"title":"2020-01-28","virtualPath":"/Diary/","html":"<p>和倉のログがなかなか拾えないな。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>ドッコラー -&gt; ドテッコツ -&gt; ローブシン</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/e3f3b2db4587b2306cc9f315a0867f75d5352e72/68747470733a2f2f696d672e67616d65776974682e6a702f61727469636c655f746f6f6c732f706f6b656d6f6e676f2f67616368612f33363337302e706e67\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/e3f3b2db4587b2306cc9f315a0867f75d5352e72/68747470733a2f2f696d672e67616d65776974682e6a702f61727469636c655f746f6f6c732f706f6b656d6f6e676f2f67616368612f33363337302e706e67\" alt=\"ドテッコツ\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.gamewith.jp/article_tools/pokemongo/gacha/36370.png\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/ef4917de03c4f714ac38972108142106efc1ca3b/68747470733a2f2f696d672e67616d65776974682e6a702f61727469636c655f746f6f6c732f706f6b656d6f6e676f2f67616368612f33363336392e706e67\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/ef4917de03c4f714ac38972108142106efc1ca3b/68747470733a2f2f696d672e67616d65776974682e6a702f61727469636c655f746f6f6c732f706f6b656d6f6e676f2f67616368612f33363336392e706e67\" alt=\"ローブシン\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.gamewith.jp/article_tools/pokemongo/gacha/36369.png\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>これ、両方とも撫でるのは嫌だよなぁ。やっぱドッコラーのままで最大強化して、飴あつめたら相棒切って進化するしか… そうこうしてる間にイベントがあるだろうけども。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>知ったかの雑魚ベテラン、ほんの一例。 <g-emoji class=\"g-emoji\" alias=\"middle_finger\" fallback-src=\"https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f595.png\">🖕</g-emoji> <g-emoji class=\"g-emoji\" alias=\"-1\" fallback-src=\"https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f44e.png\">👎</g-emoji></p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-01-28/20191214-065022-Screenshot_20191214_065022.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-01-28/20191214-065022-Screenshot_20191214_065022.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>生えた <g-emoji class=\"g-emoji\" alias=\"heart\" fallback-src=\"https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/2764.png\">❤️</g-emoji></p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-01-28/20200128-103050-Screenshot_20200128_103049.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-01-28/20200128-103050-Screenshot_20200128_103049.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"檜の新宮\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>どっこらー交換せいりーつ。驚きのキラで逆 Max ！！</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-01-28/20200128-100344-Screenshot_20200128-100344.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-01-28/20200128-100344-Screenshot_20200128-100344.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"ドッコラー\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"日記","updated":"2020-01-28T13:38:18","published":"2020-01-28T13:38:18"}